snippet.title: UN Human Rights Champion: Amber Heard
snippet.description:
During her trip to Geneva in October, visiting the United Nations headquarter, Amber Heard filmed this video in support of universal human rights. She's been nominated the UN Human Rights Champion thanks to her commitment as an advocate for women, children and LGBT community.
